      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TRUST ME (7) ran below best last time finishing fourth (27.81) over 488m at this track from Box 8. Ready to return to form. PAM KEEPING (4) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (30.08) in a OPEN at Cannington. Has a good record here at this journey. Can figure in the finish. WEST ON HARRY (6) has a terrific record this track and trip with three wins and one placing from four starts. Below best last time at Cannington (30.33) in a Grade 5, finishing a 4.5 lengths fifth. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. PAGE ONE NEWS (8) did a good job to finish third last time out over 520m at Cannington (30.44) in a Grade 4/5, the second top-three finish on the trot.",
